THE STATE OF FLORIDA, v. NATHANIEL H. SCHMUKLER 23 So. (2nd) 522

June Term, 1945

October 9, 1945 Division A J. Tom Watson, .Attorney General, Reeves Bowen, Assistant Attorney General; and Stanley Milledge, State Attorney, for appellant. Mitchell D. Price, Zaring & Florence, for appellee. PER CURIAM:

The judgment appealed from is affirmed.

CHAPMAN, C. J., TERRELL, BUFORD and ADAMS, JJ., concur.
